headline: Trump’s Bid To End Suit Is Rejected
abstract: Ms. Carroll, a writer who claims the president raped her in the 1990s, says that his denials have hurt her reputation and career.
lead_paragraph: A New York judge has rebuffed President Trump’s bid to throw out a lawsuit filed against him by the writer E. Jean Carroll, who accuses him of hurting her career and reputation in denying her claim that he raped her in a Manhattan department store in the 1990s.
